0:16:28.26,000 --> 0:16:3,000
Here's the Pacific

409
0:16:30.26,000 --> 0:16:33,000
with large MPAs

410
0:16:33.26,000 --> 0:16:36,000
and large conservation zones on it.

411
0:16:37.26,000 --> 0:16:39,000
And as you can see,

412
0:16:39.26,000 --> 0:16:42,000
we have a patchwork across this ocean.

