0:16:51.26,000 --> 0:16:53,000
And what we need to do now

418
0:16:53.26,000 --> 0:16:55,000
is look at the whole Pacific Ocean

419
0:16:55.26,000 --> 0:16:57,000
in its entirety

420
0:16:57.26,000 --> 0:16:59,000
and make a network of MPAs

421
0:16:59.26,000 --> 0:17:01,000
across the Pacific

